import React from 'react' import Button from './Button' import { useHistory } from 'react-router' import { observer } from 'mobx-react' import store from '../Stores/storeVehicle' type props = { img: any, name: string, price: string, company: string, } const Card = ( { img, name, price, company, }: props ) => { const history = useHistory() function addVehicle() { const vehicle = { img, name, price, company, } store.addVehicle(vehicle) console.log(vehicle) history.push('/checkout') } return (

{name}

{price}

addVehicle()} >
) } export default observer(Card)
